## Low Severity

### 9. General Fixture — `_logger` field (line 11, 19)

`_logger` is initialized in `[TestInitialize]` but **no test method references it**. Every test pays the cost of creating a `FakeLogger` it doesn't need.

**Fix:** Remove `_logger` from the shared fixture. Add it locally in any future test that needs it.

